{
  "stem": "734.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were two Gusens.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First, they shipped me to Gusen One, for to be processed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then Gusen Two, which was the Messerschmitt plant, the airplane plant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is-- was the last camp I was at.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was secret to a point.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was kind of wild, really, what I did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For some reason-- Well, first, I did operate a planer for a while.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Except that I was-- the planer was so bad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This-- this planer had a fault.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "For some reason, it wasn't leveled.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I had a lot of problems.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were breaking-- I was breaking a lot of knives.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The overseer, who was a civilian man, an Austrian man, a decent guy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Apparently, he must have been decent, or else he wouldn't do all these things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had this luck with decent people, [LAUGHS] which is kind of rare.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He realized that I'm breaking too many knives.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And these knives were tipped with the hardest steel, vanadium, which they couldn't produce any longer, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because their plants got knocked out, bombed out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They had to buy this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "As far as we knew, they had to purchase the steel from Sweden, which was very expensive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Those knives were tipped with the vanadium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Once you break a knife, you're out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know, you have to-- to-- to replace it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he was afraid that eventually, they'll shoot me for it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he one day-- this was late 1944, late fall of '44.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Messerschmitt realized that if he's not-- if they are not going to do something about food, some supplement, food rations, that at some point, nobody will be left to do the work.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People were dying like mad, left and right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were undernourished.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
